---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Mental Wellness & Relationship Services (MWRS)"
  description="Learn how Mental Wellness & Relationship Services (MWRS) collects, protects, and uses personal information for counseling, telehealth, and medication management services."
>
  <main class="subpage">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="subpage-hero">
      <div class="subpage-hero-inner">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy explains how Mental Wellness &amp; Relationship
          Services (MWRS) collects, uses, and protects your information when
          you visit our website or contact our team. Your privacy matters, and
          we are committed to handling your information responsibly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Policy Content -->
    <section class="subpage-section">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>
          We collect information that you voluntarily provide, such as your
          name, email address, and phone number when you fill out our online
          forms. We may also receive basic technical data such as your browser
          type, device information, and anonymized website analytics.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use your information</h2>
        <p>
          Information submitted through our website is used solely for the
          purpose of responding to your inquiry and providing services you have
          requested. We do not sell or share your personal information with
          third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>How your information is protected</h2>
        <p>
          MWRS uses secure systems, access controls, and administrative
          safeguards to help protect your information. Only authorized staff
          members involved in scheduling or care coordination have access to
          submission details.
        </p>

        <h2>HIPAA and clinical information</h2>
        <p>
          If you become a client, your clinical information is protected under
          the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA). We
          follow all federal and state regulations regarding confidentiality and
          health information.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may use analytics or embedded tools to understand how users
          interact with our site. These tools do not give us access to your
          private messages, clinical information, or other identifying data
          unless you explicitly provide it.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>
          You may contact us at any time to request updates or corrections to
          your information. If you prefer not to submit information through the
          website, you may call our office directly instead.
        </p>

        <h2>Updates to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be
          posted on this page with an updated effective date.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have questions about this policy, please contact us using the
          form below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="subpage-section subpage-cta">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Need to reach us?</h2>
        <p>
          You can contact our team with questions about scheduling, policies, or
          services. Weâ€™re here to help.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn">
          Contact us
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .subpage {
      background: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .subpage-hero {
      padding: 10rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      background: #fbfbf9;
         background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-hero-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subpage-hero h1 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-hero p {
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #0f172a;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0f172a;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);
      transition: background 0.15s ease,
                  color 0.15s ease,
                  box-shadow 0.15s ease,
                  transform 0.15s ease;
    }

    .subpage-btn:hover {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.2);
    }

    .subpage-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 3.2rem;
      background: #e5e9f3;
           background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-cta {
      background: #fbfbf9;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);
    }

    .subpage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .subpage-section h2 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section p {
      margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section ul {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section li + li {
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .subpage-cta p {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>